Bonds’s Ex-Partner Spoke to Doctor About Balco Raid

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-04-05T18:21:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/bonds-s-ex-partner-spoke-to-doctor-about-balco-raid-correct-.html
(Corrects to former business partner in first paragraph.)  Barry Bonds ’s former business
partner spoke with the slugger’s doctor in 2003 about a federal
steroids raid on a California lab and told the physician news
reports said his patient was “the main one that they supply
stuff to,” according to a transcript of a tape recording filed
in federal court today in  San Francisco .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Gullo in San Francisco
at   kgullo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at   mhytha@bloomberg.net . 